quran[10]{c,v,t}:
  75,31,Falā Şaddaqa Wa Lā Şallá
  75,32,Wa Lakin Kadhaba Wa Tawallá
  75,33,Thumma Dhahaba 'Ilá 'Ahlihi Yatamaţţá
  75,34,Awlá Laka Fa'awlá
  75,35,Thumma 'Awlá Laka Fa'awlá
  75,36,Ayaĥsabu Al-'Insānu 'An Yutraka Sudáan
  75,37,Alam Yaku Nuţfatan Min Manīyin Yumná
  75,38,Thumma Kāna `Alaqatan Fakhalaqa Fasawwá
  75,39,Faja`ala Minhu Az-Zawjayni Adh-Dhakara Wa Al-'Unthá
  75,40,Alaysa Dhālika Biqādirin `Alá 'An Yuĥyiya Al-Mawtá